See `docs/skills/runtime-oracle.md`.

Commands:
- `bun run runtime:oracle` — full parity summary
- `bun run runtime:grep -- "<pattern>"` — search for specific symbols
- `bun run runtime:extract` — extract the full bundle

The installed runtime is the source of truth when docs, types, and behavior disagree.
